Hey there, <@U25C65C3S> and <@U021RA7HR34> the issue is actually in your serverless.json file. You’re declaring endpoints which do not have real files listed:
• lead-register-link.js does not exist
• csv-download-graphql.js does not exist.
Remove them from your serverless function file and I believe it should allow you to deploy.
FWIW an error response would be nice :slightly_smiling_face: even if in the console
Agree, already went ahead and suggested that to the team. That certainly would prevent a bit of headache.
